{"updated_at": "2013-04-23T08:14:45Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2013-04-23T08:14:45Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/16845049", "id": 16845049, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5328", "issue_id": 5328, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/liufengyun", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "3efdc6b2619e57f40ce9a571fb94a739", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/3efdc6b2619e57f40ce9a571fb94a739?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F23d158e8d9bf90cb25ba9749f71fdbdc.png", "id": 754633, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/events{/privacy}", "login": "liufengyun", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/liufengyun/followers"}, "body": "I also encountered this problem when I'm using pjax and meanwhile doing action cache without layout(`caches_action xxx, :layout => false`).\r\n\r\nTo walk around this problem, I created an 'empty' layout, and set `layout` to `empty` for pjax request:\r\n\r\n``` haml\r\n/empty.html.haml\r\n=yield\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt worked as a temporary solution for me.", "_id": {"$oid": "523819c6bd3543c15100e26d"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5328#issuecomment-16845049"}
